{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState","preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNAnnotationViewDragState","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"dragState"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can override this method to animate a custom annotation view as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"drags it. As the system detects user actions that would indicate a drag, it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calls this method to update the drag state.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:animated:"}],"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L279"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setDragState:animated:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"setDragState:animated:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setDragState:animated:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setDragState:animated:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:","title":"setDragState:animated:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationViewDragState":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationviewdragstate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState","title":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"These constants indicate the current drag state of an annotation view.","type":"text"}]}}}